name: Partenope
description: Cactvs in Naples! I have been living in Naples since I was born and yet I have never been able to define myself as Neapolitan, this place offers me only discomfort fear and inadequacy nothing more, not even for a moment it was my home, despite this I can not take my eyes off the brutal beauty that surrounds it fascinates me like a moth attracted by the same light that will mark its departure
